  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large clay pot, heat the coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and sauté for 1-2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook for 5 minutes until they release their moisture and start to brown.",
    "Add the coconut milk, nutritional yeast, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the pot to the preheated oven and bake for 20-25 minutes until the mushrooms are tender and the liquid has thickened.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
